  "texts": [
    "Foreword AI and Industry-Facing the ChallengesThere is no doubt that recent developments in AI are set to make a significant industrial impact in future years.",
    "The advent of generative AI methods and specifically the subset referred to as Large Language Models (LLMs) are rapidly influencing the ability to rapid assimilate text, images and data into an organized structure appear to be a watershed in the evolution of AI.",
    "Many (and possibly most) industrial organizations are experimenting with the simple and accessible tools becoming available-often freely so-as providers seek data for their models, learnings about their usefulness and of course, market share for their products!",
    "And it is clear that this is just the beginning.The aim of this short note is to try to put industrial AI into the perspective of other-related digital systems developments, to identify some of the challenges and projects (a little) into the future!",
    "Yet AI has been in industrial use since the 1980s."
